# 6. Naming Convention NC- (R01 — CRÍTICO)
LEXICO: #naming-convention #nc-prefix #r01 #tool #svc #lbe #scr #ds #led #boot

**Formato:** `NC-<TIPO>-<SIGLA>-<NUM>-<desc>.<ext>`

| Tipo | Descrição | Exemplos |
|------|-----------|---------|
| `TOOL` | MCP Tool Python | NC-TOOL-FR-043-litellm.py |
| `SVC`  | Serviço Core    | NC-SVC-FR-020-lexico-service.py |
| `LBE`  | Lobe de Memória | NC-LBE-FR-LITELLM-001.mdc |
| `SCR`  | Script         | NC-SCR-FR-110-litellm-startup.ps1 |
| `DS`   | Ticket/Dataset  | NC-DS-131-ticket.yaml |
| `LED`  | Ledger/Dict    | NC-LED-FR-002-lexico-dictionary.json |
| `BOOT` | Boot/Config    | NC-BOOT-FR-001-system-manifest.md |
| `GOV`  | Governança YAML | NC-GOV-FR-003-ia-governance-rules.yaml |
| `CFG`  | Configuração   | NC-CFG-FR-002-rules-policy.yaml |
| `TPL`  | Template       | NC-TPL-FR-001-template-central-index.yaml |
| `TODo` | Roadmap        | NC-TODO-FR-001-project-roadmap-consolidated.md |

**NUNCA** criar arquivo sem prefixo NC-. Sem exceções.

